00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,120
 dobra

546
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,660
 a što ti radiš tamo mama

547
00:15:29,660 --> 00:15:30,920
 šta radiš uopće tamo

548
00:15:30,920 --> 00:15:33,240
 pa molim za susjedovu djecu

549
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:34,620
 a ne ne ne

550
00:15:34,620 --> 00:15:37,040
 a doslov se mi je tako rekla

551
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:38,800
 pa evo vidi ima i više

552
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:40,620
 a nas ima sedmero

553
00:15:40,620 --> 00:15:41,680
 a tamo ima više

554
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:42,980
 zato što je samo jedno više

555
00:15:42,980 --> 00:15:45,360
 dakle

556
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:47,100
 to je vrlo bitno

557
00:15:47,100 --> 00:15:48,300
 drugim riječima

558
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:50,620
 baka je djetov djedovi

559
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:52,500
 pa molite da vaši unuci

560
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:53,300
 budu svećenik

561
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:54,580
 redovnica, redovnik

562
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:57,060
 jer gospodin ih treba

563
00:15:57,060 --> 00:15:58,440
 gospodina sve treba

564
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,020
 da poziv je

565
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:00,840
 biti u braku

566
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,620
 a jednako je poziv biti

567
00:16:02,620 --> 00:16:04,640
 redovnik, redovnica, svećenik

568
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:06,360
 molite gospodara djetve

569
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:08,180
 da pošale radnike u djetvu svoju

570
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:10,060
 da bismo mi živjeli

571
00:16:10,060 --> 00:16:12,200
 od kruha koji je život

572
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,600
 ako nemamo svećenika

573
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:16,100
 mi smo gotovi

574
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:18,220
 ne bismo bili ovdje

575
00:16:18,220 --> 00:16:20,860
 ne možemo svi biti svećenici

576
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:23,940
 ali ima koji mogu biti

577
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:24,820
 ako molimo

578
00:16:24,820 --> 00:16:26,920
 za to zvanje

579
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:28,180
 dakle tri bitne stvari

580
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:28,760
 na kraju

581
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:29,560
 ispadne

582
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:31,360
 kako da vam se odužim

583
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:33,240
 za koga živim svoj život

584
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:35,200
 molim li za duhom nazvanja

585
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,320
 Amen

